Edward Nnachi, Abakaliki A student of Ebonyi State University Abakaliki,  Ikechukwu Oke, has been  hospitalised after  allegedly fasting and praying for  41  days. According to Christian Nwaokpa, a student of the university, claimed   Oke decided to embark on the  spiritual exercise because of the  challenges facing  his family. Nwaokpa  said, “He is  from Ebiaji in Ezza North LGA. It  is his nature. “As it stands now, men of goodwill and ambassadors are on the way conveying him to the Accident and Emergency Ward in Federal Teaching Hospital in Abakaliki.” Copyright PUNCH.
